        "### Hybrid: SMOTE + RUS\n",
        "\n",
        "First apply SMOTE to generate synthetic minority samples, then apply random undersampling to the majority class. This aims to reduce the information loss from pure RUS without leaning as hard on a fully synthetic or fully balanced sample."
      ],
